                div(class='col-sm-6 col-lg-4')
                    div(class='feature-block')
                        img(src='/static/images/landing-page/users.svg' alt='')
                        div(class='title') Suitable for creatives and industries such as
                        div(class='detail') AV Technicians, Event Producers, Musicians, Hair & Make-up Artists, Film, Radio, Barristers, Set Builders and Visual Merchandisers, just to name a few.
