                    div(class='feature-block')
                        img(src='/static/images/landing-page/briefcase.svg' alt='')
                        div(class='title') Looking for work?
                        div(class='detail') Register as a candidate to easily apply for jobs that interest you. Keep in touch with preferred employers.
